data.description: Welcome to Ridgeview Park Estates!  This gorgeous custom home boasts unobstructed views! Overlooking portions of riverside state park, this home is designed with elegance, luxury, and comfort in mind, perfect for someone that loves to entertain. As you enter the home you are greeted by a spacious living room that features vaulted ceilings, inviting fireplace, and large windows that provide an uninterrupted view of the magnificent Spokane landscape. The fully equipped kitchen is complete with high-end stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, and granite countertops. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, featuring a comfortable sitting area and an ensuite bathroom with a jacuzzi tub and a separate shower. The large windows offer panoramic views, creating a peaceful and serene atmosphere. The backyard is a wonderful place to spend warm summer evenings and a great place to watch fireworks! Ask your agent about potential 1.75% lender credit!
